START

Open Program Menu

Ask user option they want to use

If option is 1 - Input Data:
    Ask user for Initial Investment Amount
    Ask user for monthly deposit
    Ask user for annual interest rate
    Ask user for number of years

Next handle all calculations required
Calculate future value of investment

Loop back to start if user wants to continue

If user selects option 2:
    Output investment report without monthly deposit
    Loop back to start

If user selects option 3:
    Output investment report with monthly deposit
    Loop back to start
If user selects option 4:
    End application
END


